्योग","title":"कवर किए गए क्षेत्र","construction":"निर्माण","horeca":"होटल और रेस्टोरेंट","agriculture":"कृषि","manufacturing":"विनिर्माण","logistics":"परिवहन"},"contact":{"label":"संपर्क","title":"बात करते हैं","description":"चाहे आप स्टाफ की तलाश में नियोक्ता हों या अवसर की तलाश में उम्मीदवार, हम मदद के लिए यहां हैं।","address":"पता","phone":"फोन","email":"ईमेल","schedule":"समय","scheduleValue":"सोमवार - शुक्रवार: 09:00 - 18:00","form":{"name":"पूरा नाम","email":"ईमेल","phone":"फोन","subject":"विषय","message":"संदेश","privacy":"मैं स्वीकार करता हूं","privacyLink":"गोपनीयता नीति","send":"संदेश भेजें","sending":"भेजा जा रहा है..."}},"footer":{"description":"रोमानिया, ऑस्ट्रिया और सर्बिया में अंतर्राष्ट्रीय भर्ती एजेंसी। एशिया और अफ्रीका में 11 भागीदार।","quickLinks":"त्वरित लिंक","industries":"उद्योग","contactInfo":"संपर्क","rights":"सर्वाधिकार सुरक्षित।","privacy":"गोपनीयता नीति"},"cta":{"employer":"मैं एक नियोक्ता हूं","candidate":"मैं नौकरी ढूंढ रहा हूं"},"common":{"learnMore":"अधिक जानें","getStarted":"अभी शुरू करें","submit":"जमा करें","cancel":"रद्द करें","loading":"लोड हो रहा है...","error":"एक त्रुटि हुई","success":"सफलता!","required":"आवश्यक फ़ील्ड"},"howItWorks":{"title":"How the GJC Process Works","subtitle":"Discover the simple steps we take together to ensure the best outcome for your company or career.","tabs":{"companies":"For Companies","candidates":"For Candidates","immigration":"Immigration Services"},"steps":{"companies":{"step1":"Registration and VAT Check","step2":"Post worker requirements","step3":"Receive GJC-selected candidates","step4":"Interview and final selection","step5":"GJC handles the IGI file","step6":"The worker arrives to you ✅"},"candidates":{"step1":"Registration and profile completion","step2":"Upload documents (passport, diplomas)","step3":"Matching with suitable jobs","step4":"Interview with the employer","step5":"GJC handles the visa and permit","step6":"You leave for your new job ✅"},"immigration":{"step1":"Free consultation